Fantastic work, just what I need. Will give you a extra section in my credits ^.^<br><br>Found two tiny bugs: When your text starts with a line break ("\nMy text") then it prints just nothing and RowCount is 0. I solved this just by removing the line breaks at the start of the string.<br><br>In function <em class="text-italics">text.new</em>, when you give a non string to parameter <em class="text-italics">str</em> it chrashes. I solved this by add a <em class="text-italics">tostring</em> at the call <em class="text-italics">createRowStrings(t,<span style="color:#FF0040">tostring(str)</span>,taghandlers)</em><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=112828">Ratchet</a> — Mon Mar 17, 2014 7:51 pm</p><hr />
